title: Flow Yoga Strength & Flexibility with Monica Gonzalo [MP4]
description:
Get into shape & rejuvenate with Flow Yoga - Strength & Flexibility. This expertly designed total-body program delivers unparalleled quality & value with 8 targeted and effective flow yoga routines. These fun and engaging workouts will challenge & transform your entire body, including your core, legs, hips & arms. Experience yoga in a whole new way that increases your strength, flexibility & energy levels while reducing stress.

Includes 8 expert instructional routines:

- Warm-up (10 minutes)

- General Flow (20 Minutes)

- Core Strength (45 Minutes)

- Legs (40 Minutes)

- Arms (40 Minutes)

- Hips (45 Minutes)

- Back (35 Minutes)

- Cool Down (18 Minutes)

Filmed near stunningly beautiful glacier national park.
